<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/565110-anyone-have-an-opinion-as-to-what-is-the">Anyone have an opinion as to what is the best English translation? I bought a volume of the Cary translation (still in the mail) which I realize is written in archaic English, but it might be nice to have a more modern version as well.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_565110'><a id="like_count_community_question_565110" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/565110?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">6 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F6656.The_Divine_Comedy">like</a></span>

