<div id="review_3160437862" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3160437862" />
    <a title="Quirkyreader" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/5355311-quirkyreader"><img alt="Quirkyreader" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1452716553p2/5355311.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3160437862?book_show_action=true">Mar 14, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Quirkyreader" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Quirkyreader" href="/user/show/5355311-quirkyreader">Quirkyreader</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9780785834588" href="/book/show/30212569-the-divine-comedy">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3160437862" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer954472171577962098">This book was full of Oh My moments. And yes I had my pencil out doing annotations with this one.<br/><br/>This long poem reminded me of “The Revelation of St. John The Divine” AKA “The Book of Revelation”. <br/><br/>The super bonuses of this book were that it was the Longfellow translation and had all of the Dore illustrations.<br/><br/>Take time to read this one if you haven’t.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


